  <h2>Steps</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Provision VM/host; static IP; join voice/servers VLAN.</li>
    <li>Install Docker + Caddy; open TCP 80/443 inbound only.</li>
    <li>Set Caddyfile for <code>voice.quirkcars.com</code>; Let’s Encrypt auto-issue.</li>
    <li>Deploy WebSocket gateway container; set <code>OPENAI_API_KEY</code>.</li>
    <li>Test with Twilio trial number; validate logs and TLS chain.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Firewall</h2>
  <ul><li>Egress allow-list: OpenAI, Twilio, Let’s Encrypt (and Cloudflare DNS if used).</li></ul>

